{
  "title": "Deliciously Dense Australian Corn Tacos",
  "description": "A rich and snappy one-pot Australian dish featuring corn tortillas, this recipe is Buddhist-temple-friendly and perfect for a weeknight dinner. It combines the flavors of Australia with the simplicity of a taco.",
