    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced red onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the diced red bell pepper and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in the sweet corn kernels, smoked paprika, salt, and pepper, and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the cooked black beans to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Warm the corn tortillas by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "Assemble the tacos by spooning the corn and bean mixture onto a tortilla and garnishing with chopped cilantro.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
